                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Griscom</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Griscom reports that the departure of the Russian minister will take place
                    on the 12th instant.)</p>
